dc9f8f91b7e4094aa78e7862.jpg", "head_cover": "", "content": "电视剧《爱情公寓》由韦正导演、汪远编剧，娄艺潇、王传君、陈赫、孙艺洲等一众年轻演员担纲主演，围绕一幢名叫“爱情公寓”的普通出租式青年公寓，讲叙了公寓内四男三女之间所发生的形形色色搞笑、离奇、浪漫、感人的故事。本剧在叙事上采用创新的多线并进，试图打破传统中国情景喜剧单线式模式。播出以来即以轻松幽默的氛围、时尚潮流的形象、温馨浪漫的基调引发收视热潮，占据了年轻人观众的眼球，成为当年最受关注的电视剧之一。", "short_content": "", "type": 3, "state": 0, "ctime": 1436866637, "count": {"view": 0, "use": 0, "atten": 0}, "is_atten": 0, "likes": 0, "hates": 0, "attribute": 0, "liked": 0, "hated": 0, "extra_attr": 1}, "day_count": 1}, "19913": {"data": {"tag_id": 19913, "tag_name": "童年回忆", "cover": "", "head_cover": "", "content": "", "short_content": "", "type": 3, "state": 0, "ctime": 1436866637, "count": {"view": 0, "use": 0, "atten": 0}, "is_atten": 0, "likes": 0, "hates": 0, "attribute": 0, "liked": 0, "hated": 0, "extra_attr": 1}, "day_count": 1}, "11265": {"data": {"tag_id": 11265, "tag_name": "手工", "cover": "http://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/14387036f432cbc08a3c40662ea81ac49bdc0945.jpg", "head_cover": "http://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/aed17e61786bc61f64e71abe32436540b9fb38f0.jpg", "content": "我有一双巧手，让生活更有情趣~", "short_content": "为什么你们的手如此优秀~", "type": 3, "state": 0, "ctime": 1436866637, "count": {"view": 0, "use": 0, "atten": 0}, "is_atten": 0, "likes": 0, "hates": 0, "attribute": 0, "liked": 0, "hated": 0, "extra_attr": 0}, "day_count": 1}, "91041157": {"data": {"tag_id": 91041157, "tag_name": "安克UV打印机", "cover": "", "head_cover": "", "content": "", "short_content": "", "type": 1, "state": 0, "ctime": 1773047908, "count": {"view": 0, "use": 0, "atten": 0}, "is_atten": 0, "likes": 0, "hates": 0, "attribute": 0, "liked": 0, "hated": 0, "extra_attr": 0}, "day_count": 1}, "91041178": {"data": {"tag_id": 91041178, "tag_name": "安克E1", "cover": "", "head_cover": "", "content": "", "short_content": "", "type": 1, "state": 0, "ctime": 1773047929, "count": {"view": 0, "use": 0, "atten": 0}, "is_atten": 0, "likes": 0, "hates": 0, "attribute": 0, "liked": 0, "hated": 0, "extra_attr": 0}, "day_count": 1}, "91041191": {"data":